reviewText: Fantastic dvd! Key West's best photographer takes you on a great tour of Key West past and present. Highly recommended!!!!!

Sit down with a drink and enjoy the pictures and music on this DVD. It brought us back and made us feel like we were there again.
Great pictures !!!!

This dvd is excellent! The photos are incredible and it seems to all of the family members who have viewed it, sometimes the photos change and you see new ones ! We bought two copies and use it for relaxation.
